org.apache.hadoop.fs

Class TestHarFileSystemBasics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.TestHarFileSystemBasics

  • public class TestHarFileSystemBasics
extends Object
    This test class checks basic operations with HarFileSystem including various initialization cases, getters, and modification methods. NB: to run this test from an IDE make sure the folder "hadoop-common-project/hadoop-common/src/main/resources/" is added as a source path. This will allow the system to pick up the "core-default.xml" and "META-INF/services/..." resources from the class-path in the runtime.
